<div class="com-share" data-id="8401" data-title="《互联网金融真火，连卖鞭炮的都冲进来了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/8401/medium/8401.jpg?1436694560" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/8401.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
